{"tid":2517870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩！ 屌你正呀喂！！！","createTime":"2021-05-05T15:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T15:19:58.000Z","uid":245819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b377c5a047e608112bc4b365b6c41539ddc4e3f","tid":2517870,"uid":245819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:01:41.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！男嘅博！女嘅索！睇到硬晒！<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbE2hYB2EcoJ1KYZYicR7WL1K5zxXKEtmaYHX8k6Drsnq?filename=RNHePuR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRNHePuR.gif&h=beada8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210505/YC75UXTGDJHCPEZ6Y2ONGFBLGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210505%2FYC75UXTGDJHCPEZ6Y2ONGFBLGY%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=24e50547\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210505%2FYC75UXTGDJHCPEZ6Y2ONGFBLGY%2F&h=cafd5e0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210505/YC75UXTGDJHCPEZ6Y2ONGFBLGY/</a><br />\n李華華Online｜中銀食過返尋味 員工總行再跳大媽舞拍MV<br />\n中銀香港（2388）嘅企業金融服務部員工，早前喺總行跳舞兼且Rapper上身，拍咗個MV中環銀行界瘋傳，但呢個Team Building活動似乎唔能夠凝聚士氣，反而引來唔少業界gossip。<br />\n但中銀員工似乎冇有怕，食過返尋味，近日網上再流出一條改編自《難兄難弟》嘅MV，片中唔少衣著花俏嘅員工喺度跳舞，好似返咗去上世紀80年代咁款，但論聲音、畫質比上一次MV低，大家可以睇片評下理。<br />\n華華收到風，片段疑似係中銀總行小區為咗Annual Dinner而拍嘅片，MV入面係總行同事，包括客戶經理同埋前線，Annual Dinner原定6月以Zoom形式進行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXQGVkQmC6Zyd6aNpP4FFQrtTwYzUeGubf2cYXmHXN4aC?filename=ASbZ0x8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FASbZ0x8.gif&h=7f42a4a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb1HgBmM4eKXN538Uk7vmgUWLrdHg2YhbmmTmEYnR5puV?filename=Zr3YwEY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZr3YwEY.gif&h=b945da48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUBKkq2hc4XmjqgUqeSv83bK7Zvpi8yY7MjzWjrmg6woH?filename=FLpAyTr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLpAyTr.gif&h=5a3bce99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXFphedBFGLxFJT5HLDrjWua2cZqPVxcdD5HNqxwA3TX2?filename=dNtYwFj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNtYwFj.gif&h=32ffa98c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXaAB82u9gxB2V5QHGa8xcFacY5RErGCDGQ6cZwoSe1gs?filename=41F79r3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41F79r3.gif&h=cb079025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfCYGpSKq32ttTNrJiRwgwCLkX2SrpHbJ5fkWR8m54MKE?filename=jQwnYku.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQwnYku.gif&h=9b6d769c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbdeCWxQpXPf98h5pZgTNZkhGAFgdYEiksmBQj9ak7wyr?filename=LZzT40E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZzT40E.gif&h=4cbbeb31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPUX98qZ3jg5j6Bb6iJkiiigw3wrQX2aCoTm5AjwUxByJ?filename=Y9P1uso.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9P1uso.gif&h=30c72b81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZmJF2vKAigyZsixz1ppQCvgub49uiVSWoj6McxAGSeFi?filename=RFLzPss.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFLzPss.gif&h=9c606bfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b27e836a1cfc86ac6808195035df70cd11922e0","tid":2517870,"uid":362366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:14:05.000Z","msg":"本來想講香港打工仔RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但中銀員工就算撚數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續跳多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse